phic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Tucker|2011|p=340}}\n* [[Martin B-57 Canberra|RB-57 Canberra]] - tactical photographic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=100-105}}\n* [[B-66 Destroyer|RB-66]] - tactical photographic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=56-59}}\n* [[F-4|RF-4 Phantom II]] - carrier and land-based tactical photographic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=112-117}}\n* [[Vought F-8 Crusader|RF-8 Crusader]] - carrier-based tactical photographic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=158-159}}\n* [[McDonnell F-101 Voodoo|RF-101 Voodoo]] - tactical photographic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=118-119}}\n* [[Lockheed T-33|RT-33A]] - reconnaissance jet{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|p=11}}\n* [[Grumman S-2 Tracker|S-2 Tracker]] - carrier-based anti-submarine warfare (ASW) aircraft\n* [[Lockheed SR-71 Blackbird|SR-71 Blackbird]] - strategic reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=96-97}}\n* [[Grumman F-9 Cougar|TF-9J Cougar]] - fast forward air controller{{citation needed|date=December 2018}}\n* [[North American T-28 Trojan|T-28 Trojan]] - trainer/ground attack aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=132-133}}\n* [[Cessna T-41 Mescalero|T-41 Mescalero]] - trainer aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|2001|p=161}}\n* [[de Havilland Canada DHC-3 Otter|U-1 Otter]] - transport aircraft{{sfn|Robinson|1983|p=61}}\n* [[Lockheed U-2|U-2]] - reconnaissance aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|pp=98-99}}\n* [[de Havilland Canada DHC-2 Beaver|U-6 Beaver]] - utility aircraft{{sfn|Tucker|2011|p=22}}\n* [[Beechcraft L-23 Seminole|U-8 Seminole]] - transport/electronic survey aircraft{{sfn|Robinson|1983|p=61}}{{sfn|Nalty|2001|p=148}}\n* [[Helio Courier|U-10 Helio Courier]] - utility aircraft{{sfn|Tucker|2011|p=22}}\n* [[Cessna 185 Skywagon|U-17 Skywagon]] - utility aircraft{{sfn|Nalty|Watson|Neufeld|1981|p=15}}\n* [[Beechcraft King Air|U-21 Ute]] - liaison an